<div class="language-javascript codeBlockContainer_xCgK theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QzcU"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-javascript codeBlock_eICo thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_S361"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">不会写太基础的东西，因为自行 </span><span class="token maybe-class-name">Google</span><span class="token plain"> 就可以。我要写的一定是以体系化的，而且要能直达技术的本质。</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_kgaP"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_O83D" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_C2Wz"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_MBW4"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
